<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #343a40;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .admin-btn {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: white;
        }

        .order-btn {
            background-color: #007bff;
        }

        .order-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .coupon-btn {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }

        .coupon-btn:hover {
            background-color: #1e7e34;
        }

        .support-btn {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: black;
        }

        .support-btn:hover {
            background-color: #e0a800;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>관리자 사이트</h1>

<div class="button-container">
    <button class="admin-btn order-btn" onclick="location.href='/admin/orders'">주문 처리</button>
    <button class="admin-btn coupon-btn" onclick="location.href='/admin/coupons'">쿠폰 관리</button>
    <button class="admin-btn support-btn" onclick="location.href='/admin/support'">상담 처리</button>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
